title: Ebro In The Morning - Kanye West On Fox News + House Of Dragons Hype
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 10/7/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio talking about the Kanye West Fox News interview, apple picking, House of Dragons and so much more!

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
